        <updateDate>2021-09-15T20:24:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Natural Cosmetics Act </b></p>  <p>This bill prohibits the sale of a cosmetics product that uses the term <i style="">natural</i> on its packaging or labeling unless the product meets certain requirements. The bill also authorizes the Food and Drug Administration to request or order a recall of a cosmetics product that violates these labeling requirements.</p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
